  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add ginger and garlic, sauté until fragrant.",
    "Add onion and red bell pepper, cook until softened.",
    "Stir in ground beef, breaking it apart, and cook until browned.",
    "Sprinkle allspice and thyme, stirring to coat the meat.",
    "Mix in tomato paste and coconut aminos, cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in beef broth and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat, cover, and simmer for 30 minutes.",
    "Stir in lime juice and adjust seasoning with salt if needed.",
    "Remove from heat, let rest 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Cook ground beef to an internal temperature of 71°C / 160°F (no longer pink in the middle) before serving."
  ],
